00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:26.900
One study breaks down three types of loneliness.

00:01:26.900 --> 00:01:31.820
Situational loneliness is when unpleasant events 
or circumstances cause us to retract from society.

00:01:31.820 --> 00:01:36.560
Developmental loneliness can hinder
our capacity to balance individualism and intimacy.

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:40.380
(Psychological disorders like depression or schizophrenia could cause developmental loneliness).

00:01:40.380 --> 00:01:43.620
And finally, internal loneliness,

00:01:43.620 --> 00:01:48.280
when a self-perception of worthlessness intensifies
the feeling of being alone.

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:50.280
